metadata.name: Come Together // Wawona
metadata.description:
"Come Together" is a limited series, showcasing the Outer Sunset in San Francisco, CA. This iconic neighborhood is full of homes painted in a wide range of colors. Every home has its own distinct identity, created through: decoration, textures, colors, and personal touches.

While exploring the neighborhood, I came across a handful of homes with unique, back to back front steps. Both homes mirroring one another, offering their own personal touches, coming together to create cohesive scene; simple, yet full of wonder.
